caption: so I wanted to enter the contest because these two mean the world to me, I haven't seen them yet but I'm so thankful to get the opportunity to see them in november, I remember when distance and flights came out and thinking oh my god I love them so much and thinking that they couldn't get better than they were already but they did, so so much better, the calibraska EP really proves that and I just want to say I'm so proud of them for who they've become and to know that they're making the type of music that THEY wanna make is the best feeling ever, they aren't being forced into being people who they aren't, and I guess I just want the opportunity to tell them all of that in person (and that I love them ofc) anyways, I love you jack and jack and keep doing what you wanna do ?? @jackandjackofficial #contest
